                "title": "鋼脊"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/5a7f4821eca7816e8d923684ccee651c_4868665737743593762.png",
                "id": "talent68027",
                "key": "利爪與蒼雷",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "利爪與蒼雷"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成5點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷狼</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷狼</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色使用普通攻擊或元素戰技後：</span>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/898eb03f9942b7b7833a3c082a86fdef_182299847198088375.png",
                "id": "talent93107",
                "key": "雷牙",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷牙"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_4885804142796849729.png",
                "id": "talent78543",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，持續回合-1；</p><p>持續回合耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_4128297255435773120.png",
